quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,"Have you not seen how your Lord dealt with the people of the elephants?",footnotes:182844:1|182845:2
  105,2,"Did He not bring their plan to naught?",footnotes:182846:1|182847:2
  105,3,"And He sent against them swarms of birds",footnotes:182848:1
  105,4,"which smote them with stones of baked clay,",footnotes:182849:1
  105,5,"and made them like straw eaten up (by cattle).",footnotes:182850:1
